---
// Follow / Subscribe CTA — placed after share bar in blog posts
---

<section class="follow-cta" aria-label="フォロー・購読">
	<div class="follow-cta-inner">
		<div class="follow-cta-glow"></div>
		<div class="follow-cta-content">
			<span class="follow-cta-icon">📬</span>
			<h3 class="follow-cta-heading">最新AI情報を見逃さない！</h3>
			<p class="follow-cta-text">
				AIトレンド速報は毎日最新のAIニュースをお届けしています。<br />
				フォロー＆購読して、最新情報をいち早くキャッチしましょう。
			</p>
			<div class="follow-cta-buttons">
				<a
					href="https://x.com/"
					target="_blank"
					rel="noopener noreferrer"
					class="follow-btn follow-btn-x"
				>
					<svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
						<path d="M18.244 2.25h3.308l-7.227 8.26 8.502 11.24H16.17l-5.214-6.817L4.99 21.75H1.68l7.73-8.835L1.254 2.25H8.08l4.713 6.231zm-1.161 17.52h1.833L7.084 4.126H5.117z"/>
					</svg>
					フォローする
				</a>
				<a
					href="/rss.xml"
					target="_blank"
					class="follow-btn follow-btn-rss"
				>
					<svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
						<path d="M6.18 15.64a2.18 2.18 0 0 1 2.18 2.18C8.36 19 7.38 20 6.18 20C5 20 4 19 4 17.82a2.18 2.18 0 0 1 2.18-2.18M4 4.44A15.56 15.56 0 0 1 19.56 20h-2.83A12.73 12.73 0 0 0 4 7.27V4.44m0 5.66a9.9 9.9 0 0 1 9.9 9.9h-2.83A7.07 7.07 0 0 0 4 12.93V10.1z"/>
					</svg>
					RSS購読
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.follow-cta {
		max-width: 760px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 0 1.5rem 2rem;
	}
	.follow-cta-inner {
		position: relative;
		overflow: hidden;
		border-radius: 16px;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0c1222 0%, #0f172a 50%, #1e293b 100%);
		padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
		text-align: center;
	}
	.follow-cta-glow {
		position: absolute;
		top: -40px;
		right: -40px;
		width: 200px;
		height: 200px;
		border-radius: 50%;
		background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.25) 0%, transparent 70%);
		pointer-events: none;
	}
	.follow-cta-content {
		position: relative;
		z-index: 1;
	}
	.follow-cta-icon {
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		display: block;
		margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
		animation: follow-bounce 2s ease-in-out infinite;
	}
	@keyframes follow-bounce {
		0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
		50% { transform: translateY(-6px); }
	}
	.follow-cta-heading {
		font-size: 1.3rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: #f1f5f9;
		margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
		line-height: 1.4;
	}
	.follow-cta-text {
		font-size: 0.88rem;
		color: #94a3b8;
		line-height: 1.7;
		margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
		max-width: 480px;
		margin-left: auto;
		margin-right: auto;
	}
	.follow-cta-buttons {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		gap: 0.75rem;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
	}
	.follow-btn {
		display: inline-flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 0.5em;
		padding: 0.7em 1.5em;
		border-radius: 10px;
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		text-decoration: none;
		transition: all 0.25s ease;
		color: white;
	}
	.follow-btn:hover {
		transform: translateY(-2px);
		color: white;
	}
	.follow-btn-x {
		background: #0f1419;
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
		box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
	}
	.follow-btn-x:hover {
		background: #1a1f25;
		box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
	}
	.follow-btn-rss {
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0ea5e9, #0284c7);
		box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.3);
	}
	.follow-btn-rss:hover {
		box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.4);
	}

	@media (max-width: 720px) {
		.follow-cta {
			padding: 0 1rem 1.5rem;
		}
		.follow-cta-inner {
			padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
		}
		.follow-cta-heading {
			font-size: 1.15rem;
		}
		.follow-cta-buttons {
			flex-direction: column;
			gap: 0.5rem;
		}
		.follow-btn {
			width: 100%;
			justify-content: center;
		}
	}
</style>
